<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><?ish ishref="GUID-5C27F974-AF2D-473F-84EB-591CA36A3CBB" version="3" lang="en-US"?><task xmlns:ditaarch="http://dita.oasis-open.org/architecture/2005/" id="GUID-5C27F974-AF2D-473F-84EB-591CA36A3CBB" xml:lang="en-US" ditaarch:DITAArchVersion="1.3" domains="(topic task)                            (topic hi-d)                            (topic ui-d)                            (topic sw-d)                            (topic indexing-d)                            (topic ut-d)                            a(base ishcondition)                            a(base varid)                            a(base varref)                            a(base cid)                            a(base partslist)                            (topic oce-d)                            (topic sdlVariables-c)                            (topic oceCommonElements-c)                            (topic oceMetaDecl-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c task oceTask-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c hi-d oceHighlight-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c ui-d oceUi-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c sw-d oceSoftware-c)   " class="- topic/topic task/task "><title class="- topic/title ">How to create an export of the TSM (in Robin)</title><prolog class="- topic/prolog "><metadata class="- topic/metadata "><category class="- topic/category ">Tools</category></metadata></prolog><taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody "><prereq id="PREREQ_42601235753940259D4B4F30A376B9DD" class="- topic/section task/prereq "><note id="GUID-E1C52EE8-1C1B-4FAE-880C-2E56B86285B9" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">You need special access rights to be able to do this.
</p></note><ul id="UL_04EFA54C9D674B008B5158FF57FDA14B" class="- topic/ul "><li id="LI_AB65684253D3407C82190797C780E183" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> A valid SAM key with sufficient storage space to store the TSM or
</p><p class="- topic/p "> a valid SAM key plus an USB key with sufficient storage space for the TSM.
</p></li><li id="LI_7F29F31F910240DC9B34D3ADC4DC994A" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Robin must be installed.
</p></li><li id="LI_AB552590302B4755BC1CA71401D782F8" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">The required encrypted version of the TSM replicated via Robin is needed
</p></li><li id="LI_199EE1DB0E7B4EA8BF554098556DB6B8" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> The role for “TSM export” in Robin is required (otherwise “Export Checked” button is not available in Robin). 
</p></li></ul></prereq><section id="SECTION_02241AC5597047B8B9BEE26FF520BE49" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Procedure</title><table id="TABLE_7E020A3B98454689AE6A18755720AF3F" class="- topic/table "><tgroup cols="2" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="10*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="90*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Step 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry></row></thead><tbody class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">1 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Connect the SAM key with internal memory or
</p><p class="- topic/p "> a valid SAM key without memory plus an USB key with sufficient space to the laptop. 
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">2 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">If needed: Rename the USB / SAM key that is going to hold the TSM to “ROBINIMPORT”. 
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">3 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Open Robin. 
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">4 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Go to the [Overview] tab. 
</p><fig id="FIG_23E793A46283487D853BEB3713D7A57D" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-1EE6D5D9-69FD-45F1-94E4-C26CCA110B97-low.png" id="IMAGE_3F42C2831E6E4C4DB38DBB059306FDCE" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-1EE6D5D9-69FD-45F1-94E4-C26CCA110B97-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">5 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Check that the TSM is up-to-date. 
</p><p class="- topic/p "> If needed: Select [Update Checked]. 
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">6 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Select the TSM and click on the [Export Checked] button. 
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">7 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">The Browse for the folder screen is shown. 
</p><fig id="FIG_1603F6DE0EFE453897D8309EDB19E03D" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-897881F8-81E1-4AAF-ABF6-A792F31214F3-low.png" id="IMAGE_9A3B6F65379C4A08940C9C1DF4284C3A" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-897881F8-81E1-4AAF-ABF6-A792F31214F3-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">8 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Select a directory on the hard disk. 
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">9 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">The TSM is exported. 
</p><fig id="FIG_7A7F683E4A314870AD7A87659B3B70B7" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-33D81E15-4E84-4C56-9802-71D3DE16108E-low.png" id="IMAGE_94346C68840D4845A2623B5A20B04F6E" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-33D81E15-4E84-4C56-9802-71D3DE16108E-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">10 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">At the end the [Export overview] is shown. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Click on the [OK] button to finish the export. 
</p><fig id="FIG_D3B2ABD3A63C461EB754E3117982CA7A" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-55C6899C-C198-4AB0-BE3B-2411004FB189-low.png" id="IMAGE_8BFCCF028E584271B97650268E76E049" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-55C6899C-C198-4AB0-BE3B-2411004FB189-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">11 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Copy the zip file to the SAM / USB key that you have prepared.
</p></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section></taskbody><related-links class="- topic/related-links "><linkpool class="- topic/linkpool " mapkeyref="GUID-8A41CFEA-5928-4042-A2CB-507A5D034160"><link class="- topic/link " mapclass="- map/topicref " format="dita" type="concept" href="generated-topic-GUID-4998CEE3-DF0A-4501-ADA0-694495243747.xml" role="parent"><?ditaot usertext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext "><?ditaot usertext?>HTML TSM on the Printer</linktext></link></linkpool></related-links>
</task>